I ran a browser session to verify:

Dashboard Appearance: Confirmed the dashboard is no longer "all-white" in dark mode.
Input Readability: Verified that search bars and chat inputs are readable (light text on dark background).
Toggle Functionality: Confirmed clicking the toggle switches themes instantly.
