Theme Persistence & Toggle Fix
Issue: Theme reverted to stored preference on navigation; Header toggle was unresponsive.
Fix:
Decoupled 
SettingsPage
 from forcing stored theme.
Updated 
ThemeToggle
 to sync changes to store.
Added z-50 to 
ThemeToggle
 to fix unresponsiveness.
Verification: Verified toggling works and persists across 
/chat
 and /settings.
